                <div1>
                    <div2>
                            <lb ed="I" n="0227a01"/>□□□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">靜</unclear>滿。<note n="0227001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB08073;＝旨【中研院】</note><app n="0227001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">旨</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB08073;</rdg></app>道圓明。言像<note n="0227002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31048;＝所【中研院】</note><app n="0227002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31048;</rdg></app>未臻。文字不能述。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">如</unclear>□□
                            <lb ed="I" n="0227a02"/>□。闢之者<note n="0227003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31067;＝既【中研院】</note><app n="0227003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">既</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31067;</rdg></app>難。法海波<note n="0227004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB07876;＝爛【中研院】</note><app n="0227004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">爛</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB07876;</rdg></app>。遊之者勿易。是大都邑主宋買
                            <lb ed="I" n="0227a03"/>廿二人等。可謂知周道濟之功。圓應遍知之&CB00528;。宗尚<note n="0227005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31050;＝莊【中研院】</note><app n="0227005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">莊</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31050;</rdg></app>老
                            <lb ed="I" n="0227a04"/>之談。景暮神仙之術。強攬博聞。<note n="0227006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30356;＝辨【中研院】</note><app n="0227006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">辨</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30356;</rdg></app>說無<note n="0227007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB01002;＝礙【中研院】</note><app n="0227007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">礙</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB01002;</rdg></app>。宣陽金口。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">深</unclear>識
                            <lb ed="I" n="0227a05"/>法相。乃祖乃父。積德於無窮。維子維孫。脩道於祇劫。故能
                            <lb ed="I" n="0227a06"/>知四毒之分<note n="0227008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31051;＝段【中研院】</note><app n="0227008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">段</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31051;</rdg></app>。五蔭之<note n="0227009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB04837;＝美【中研院】</note><app n="0227009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">美</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB04837;</rdg></app>知。遂寄財於三寶。託<note n="0227010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31052;＝果【中研院】</note><app n="0227010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">果</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31052;</rdg></app>於娑羅。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0227a07"/>磬<note n="0227011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31053;＝竭【中研院】</note><app n="0227011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">竭</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31053;</rdg></app>家珍。敬造天宮石像各一區。其天宮也。左<note n="0227012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31054;＝臨【中研院】</note><app n="0227012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">臨</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31054;</rdg></app>淥水。早
                            <lb ed="I" n="0227a08"/>有公路。<note n="0227013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00117;＝澗【中研院】</note><app n="0227013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">澗</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00117;</rdg></app>之<note n="0227014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31054;＝低【中研院】</note><app n="0227014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">低</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31054;</rdg></app>迴。右觀<note n="0227015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30921;＝舊【中研院】</note><app n="0227015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">舊</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30921;</rdg></app>都。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">快</unclear>有京華之<note n="0227016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30412;＝勢【中研院】</note><app n="0227016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">勢</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30412;</rdg></app>。前囑風嶺。<note n="0227017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30141;＝據【中研院】</note><app n="0227017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">據</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30141;</rdg></app>
                            <lb ed="I" n="0227a09"/>在曹<note n="0227018" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30535;＝操【中研院】</note><app n="0227018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">操</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30535;</rdg></app>之故&CB00100;。從背望山。伊洛之南地。私乃正是四奧之
                            <lb ed="I" n="0227a10"/>華壤。中<note n="0227019" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31055;＝墟【中研院】</note><app n="0227019"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">墟</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31055;</rdg></app>之靜土。唯非舍利神<note n="0227020" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31056;＝變【中研院】</note><app n="0227020"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">變</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31056;</rdg></app>之<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">園</unclear>。實是須達<note n="0227021" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30703;＝布【中研院】</note><app n="0227021"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">布</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30703;</rdg></app>金之
                            <lb ed="I" n="0227a11"/>地。其像也。乃運玉石於荊山。採浮磬於淮逋。鐫勒彫文。並
                            <lb ed="I" n="0227a12"/>龍鱗而翠<note n="0227022" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB03140;＝璨【中研院】</note><app n="0227022"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">璨</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB03140;</rdg></app>。鏤狀圓形。等金錦而<note n="0227023" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB15137;＝競【中研院】</note><app n="0227023"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">競</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB15137;</rdg></app>炎。<note n="0227024" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31057;＝雙【中研院】</note><app n="0227024"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">雙</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31057;</rdg></app>林見光。未殊於
                            <lb ed="I" n="0227a13"/>此妙。<note n="0227025" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30357;＝剋【中研院】</note><app n="0227025"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">剋</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30357;</rdg></app>檀成剬。有愧於<note n="0227026" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31058;＝今【中研院】</note><app n="0227026"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">今</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31058;</rdg></app>容。<note n="0227027" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31067;＝既【中研院】</note><app n="0227027"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">既</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31067;</rdg></app>如天上降來。又似地中勇
                            <lb ed="I" n="0227a14"/>出。其中万相<note n="0227028" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31050;＝莊【中研院】</note><app n="0227028"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">莊</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31050;</rdg></app><note n="0227029" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31059;＝嚴【中研院】</note><app n="0227029"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">嚴</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31059;</rdg></app>。五色鮮妙。珠紫爭光。清黃吐艷。跂看之
                            <lb ed="I" n="0227a15"/>徒。樂善妄歸。觀狀難同。<note n="0227030" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30425;＝尋【中研院】</note><app n="0227030"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">尋</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30425;</rdg></app>刑叵遍。自非高見大士。十力世
                            <lb ed="I" n="0227a16"/>雄。熟能建私功<note n="0227031" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31064;＝業【中研院】</note><app n="0227031"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">業</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31064;</rdg></app>者<note n="0227032" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31065;＝哉【中研院】</note><app n="0227032"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">哉</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31065;</rdg></app>。緣茲摩訶善根。仰發洪願。三寶常
                            <lb ed="I" n="0227a17"/>存。法輪永固。王祚<note n="0227033" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30357;＝剋【中研院】</note><app n="0227033"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">剋</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30357;</rdg></app>隆。七世先<note n="0227034" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31060;＝靈【中研院】</note><app n="0227034"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">靈</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31060;</rdg></app>。託生妙樂。見在<note n="0227035" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31060;＝眷【中研院】</note><app n="0227035"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">眷</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31060;</rdg></app>屬。值
                            <lb ed="I" n="0227a18"/>佛聞法。四生之<note n="0227036" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31066;＝類【中研院】</note><app n="0227036"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">類</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31066;</rdg></app>。等成正覺。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0227a19"/>□齊天統三年歲次丁亥四月辛丑朔八日戊申建立
                    </div2>
