                            <lb ed="I" n="0227c06"/>維<note n="0227042" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB01057;＝那【中研院】</note><app n="0227042"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">那</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB01057;</rdg></app>趙文紹
